region and classify encoded depth classes. In addition, PSO optimization was implemented to enhance performance of dete
ction model by tuning hyperparameters. To evaluate detection performance, four variances of the YOLOv5 deep learning mo
del and a two鈥恠tage Faster R鈥怌NN model were implemented. The proposed approach demonstrated that the YOLOv5L variant ac
hieved mean average precision (mAP) and intersection over union (IoU) scores of 0.99 and 0.89, respectively, whereas th
e YOLOv5S variant obtained mAP and IoU scores of 0.76 and 0.84, respectively. In addition, YOLOv5L variant showed highe
