hieved mean average precision (mAP) and intersection over union (IoU) scores of 0.99 and 0.89, respectively, whereas th
e YOLOv5S variant obtained mAP and IoU scores of 0.76 and 0.84, respectively. In addition, YOLOv5L variant showed highe
